INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES ('260', '1', '2013-07-18 13:58:35', '2013-07-18 13:58:35', '<h1>Buffalo Limo Service</h1>\r\nBuffalo New York Limousine Rental is your one-stop for luxury rentals in Buffalo, as well as surrounding cities and suburbs like Akron, Getzville, Tonawanda, Sanborn, Lockport, Crittenden, Middleport, Marilla, Elma, Gasport and East Elmherst. Our limousine service has built its reputation by providing the most exquisite transportation available in a range of sizes and styles to suit every occasion. And our limo prices are unbeatable.\r\n<table width=\"460\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/melbourne-white-hummer-limo.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-212\" alt=\"melbourne-white-hummer-limo\" src=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/melbourne-white-hummer-limo.jpg\" width=\"230\" height=\"144\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<center></center>&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Limo Service Buffalo, NY</h2>\r\nProfessional sports, arts, entertainment, cuisine and nightlife - not to mention those wings - are some of the reasons Buffalo is famous. Just 20 minutes from Niagara Falls, you can view Frank Lloyd Wright architecture, take in a Broadway-cast performance at Shea’s Performing Arts Center or enjoy modern art exhibits at the Albright-Knox Art gallery. The Buffalo Philharmonic Orchestra has won Grammy Awards, and there are tons of regular festivals, concerts and sporting events (like the Bills, Sabres and Bisons) beckoning the adventurer. There is the great outdoors and access to plenty of water sports, like fishing and skiing. Add in some great boutique shopping at Elmwood Village and Walden Galleria, along with hundreds of incredible restaurants and a truly rockin’ nightlife, and it’s easy to see why people love Buffalo.\r\n\r\nBuffalo NY Limos will pick you up in 14201, 14218, 14280 or any adjacent zip code, and we’ll treat you like the star you are. Our trained representatives are available around the clock to assist you with your selection from our fleet. We offer affordable limo prices on such elegant rentals as the Rolls Royce, Lincoln Stretch and Escalade. Our staff will provide the latest limo quotes and make sure you get the very best limo hire for your occasion, whatever the size or style you need.\r\n\r\nA stretch limo is a popular favorite for so many occasions, such as proms, corporate travel or graduation celebrations. The Chrysler 300 Stretch is a great choice for a night at the symphony or a romantic dinner at Torches Restaurant or Rue Franklin. Buffalo New York Limo also offers an exquisite wedding stretch limo in white, perfect for any bride’s vision of the perfect day. Every occasion is more memorable when your chauffeur handles the travel details, like navigation traffic and parking.\r\n<h2>Reserve A Limo Rental in Buffalo, New York</h2>\r\nTurn heads at HSBC Arena, when you and your friends arrive at the concert in your fierce Hummer Limo or Range Rover from Buffalo NY Limo Rental. Or just enjoy a night of exploring all the hot spots, like Rendezvous the Nightclub, Pure Night Club, Bottoms Up, Lux, Sky Bar, Club Marcella, Bayou, 67 West. Dance all night at Noir Ultra Lounge, Purple Monkey Tropical Pub, and Indulge. Then let your driver handle the traffic as you return safely home, enjoying every mile of the journey with your friends.\r\n\r\nBirthdays, anniversaries, bar mitzvahs and bat mitzvahs, concerts and festivals, sporting events, adventures with the kids, airport shuttle, bachelor or bachelorette parties, day trips and night outings are all great reasons to rent a Buffalo NY Limo. When you let us take the wheel, you’ll have the ride of your life.', 'box buffalo limousine service', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'box-buffalo-limousine-service', '', '', '2013-07-20 14:32:23', '2013-07-20 14:32:23', '', '0', 'http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/?page_id=260', '0', 'page', '', '0');
