INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES ('277', '1', '2013-07-18 15:25:33', '2013-07-18 15:25:33', '<h1>Anaheim Party Bus</h1>\r\nHave a wacky night on the town with an Anaheim CA party bus. If you are looking for a fun way to see the sights and sounds of the city in style, check out an Anaheim party bus. Grab your friends, call up the family and hop on board for night of excitement and thrills. With an Anaheim California party bus, you can party it up while leaving the driving to a responsible professional. You and your crew have only one task, and that is to make your night a time to remember for years to come.\r\n\r\nAn Anaheim California party bus rental enables you to enjoy the company of your guests while riding along in comfort and safety. When you let a driver take the wheel with party buses in Anaheim CA, you leave all the cares of driving behind. Parking can be hard to find or just plain expensive. Traffic is the last thing you want to deal with when trying to have a good time. Fueling up the tank takes time away from the fun. A limo bus rental enables you to forget these troubles and focus on the party. Wherever your trip takes you, even if it\'s to Villa Park, Buena Park, Tustin, Costa Mesa, or Stanton, we are your answer to luxury transportation in the area.\r\n<table width=\"460\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Hummer_limo_yellow.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-462\" alt=\"Hummer_limo_yellow\" src=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Hummer_limo_yellow-300x225.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div align=\"center\"></div>\r\n<h2>Party Buses Anaheim CA</h2>\r\nIs your group in the mood to play some pool and belt out a few karaoke tunes? Fifteens Cocktails (92804) is the place to hit. If there\'s a game your group just has to see over some cold drinks, head over to Throwbacks Sports Bar (92805). If you like to wind down at a hookah lounge, Fusion Ultra Lounge is a great spot to kick back. To dance the night away, try Heat Ultra Lounge (92802). You can rock the night away at the House of Blues to catch some music.\r\n\r\nIf you have the spirit of adventure, you can head to Buena Park, Yorba Linda or Fullerton. The clubs in these areas are frequented by friendly locals. Placentia and Garden Grove are also nearby, and you\'ll find something for everyone in Orange and Cypress. Any of these locations are close enough for a quick trip, but also give you a little down time between stops.\r\n<h2>Party Bus Prices Anaheim</h2>\r\nWith low party bus prices, you don\'t have to be concerned about cost. Limo buses in Anaheim fit into any budget. Your money should be spent on food, drink and fun. Your wallet will still be full after renting from a party bus company. It\'s easy to convince your friends to split the cost, since in Anaheim cheap party buses are available for any occasion. Weddings, bachelor parties, bachelorette night, and birthday bashes are perfect times to rent a party bus in Anaheim. Parents looking for a way to get kids to the big dance will appreciate a prom party bus in Anaheim. Rest assured that everyone will get there safely and on time.\r\n\r\nCheap party bus rentals Anaheim make any occasion special, whether you want to turn an ordinary gathering into an extraordinary adventure, or if you simply want to travel in style. Just ask the satisfied customers we\'ve hosted over the years who rave about our service and return for more. We deliver top quality, premiere class, memories that will last a lifetime.', 'Anaheim Party Bus', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'anaheim-party-bus', '', '', '2013-07-20 15:09:18', '2013-07-20 15:09:18', '', '0', 'http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/?page_id=277', '0', 'page', '', '0');
