INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES ('288', '1', '2013-07-18 15:33:08', '2013-07-18 15:33:08', '<h1>Bakersfield Party Bus</h1>\r\nIt\'s time to have a ball with a Bakersfield CA Party Bus. If you\'re looking for an exciting way to experience your favorite city, you want a fantastic celebration. When a routine trip to your local bar doesn\'t give you the same thrill, why not go with a Bakersfield party bus? With so many things to do and attractions to see, you can bump it up a notch and paint the town red with your group. Your friends and family will look back on a Bakersfield California party bus excursion with fond memories of the exciting time you\'ll have.\r\n\r\nA special occasion is a perfect opportunity to plan a Bakersfield California party bus rental. Wedding coming up? Take the crew out on the town for the bachelor/bachelorette party! Limo buses in Bakersfield will drive you to all your beloved watering holes and restaurants. You can also get the family together for your next reunion, birthday or anniversary party. When it\'s time for the big dance, a prom party bus in Bakersfield will get everyone there in style.\r\n<table width=\"460\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/whitelimo50pass.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-469\" alt=\"whitelimo50pass\" src=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/whitelimo50pass-300x227.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"227\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div align=\"center\"></div>\r\n<h2>Party Buses Bakersfield CA</h2>\r\nWith reasonable party bus prices, you can invite a crowd and still have some cash left in your wallet. But you don\'t need a special event to enjoy party buses in Bakersfield CA. With a cheap limo bus rental, you can host a fantastic party any day of the week. Everyone in your group will appreciate it when you keep the fun budget friendly.\r\n\r\nWhen you just can\'t miss the big game, Replay Lounge and Grill (93308) is the sports bar for you. If you\'re hungry, you can get some fabulous Italian food in a pub setting at Sandrini\'s (93301) or have a bit at Eureka Burger. Lengthwise Brewing Company (93313) is a must see spot for those beer aficionados in your group. Music lovers will get a kick out of Buck Owens\' Music Palace for late night tunes.\r\n<h2>Party Bus Prices Bakersfield</h2>\r\nYou won\'t need to travel too far for a spectacular time, but head in the direction of Oildale or Rosedale for a little change of pace. The trip out to Lake Isabella is a beautiful drive to enjoy some scenery while sipping martinis. Fuller Acres and Lamont are a little diversion away where you can down a few pints with some friendly locals at neighborhood taverns. You can always find a great time and some cool nightlife in Shafter or McFarland.\r\n\r\nDuring your tour, take in the wonderful sights of the big city. A party bus company does the driving while you sit back, relax and mingle. Stop for a cocktail here, and appetizer there, and tons of photo opportunities all over town. Our cheap party bus rentals Bakersfield is the best in the business. Just ask the satisfied customers we\'ve hosted over the years who rave about our service and return for more. Top quality, premiere class, memories that will last a lifetime. Bakersfield cheap party buses deliver it all.\r\n\r\nWhether you\'re ready to give your special day a jolt of fun or make an ordinary time extraordinary, rent a party bus in Bakersfield. You can celebrate in style and unwind, knowing you\'ve picked the city\'s top notch service. If your trip takes you to San Juan Capistrano, Fullerton, San Clemente, Garden Grove, or Placentia, we have you covered for any transportation needs!', 'Bakersfield Party Bus', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bakersfield-party-bus', '', '', '2013-07-20 15:09:20', '2013-07-20 15:0