INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES ('293', '1', '2013-07-18 15:37:08', '2013-07-18 15:37:08', '<h1>Cincinnati Party Bus</h1>\r\nThe party never ends on a Cincinnati OH Party Bus. When it\'s time to get together with your friends and family for an exciting night out on the town, make sure to check out party buses in Cincinnati OH. Your whole group will be entertained by the sights and attractions around the city while riding along in comfort and socializing. Limo buses in Cincinnati take over the driving duties for the journey, leaving you to do nothing but chill out with a cold one and relax.\r\n\r\nAny occasion is a perfect opportunity for a Cincinnati Ohio party bus rental. If you have a wedding coming up, you will have to get the crew together for a bachelor or bachelorette party. With all the crazy revelry that can ensue, it is wise to have a Cincinnati party bus driver at the wheel. Parents will rest assured that children are in good hands with a prom party bus in Cincinnati. An anniversary is cause to celebrate in style, and a limo bus rental will not disappoint the happy couple as they tour the city surrounded by luxury.\r\n<table width=\"460\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\r\n<a href=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/ttl-lb4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-479\" alt=\"ttl lb4\" src=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/ttl-lb4-300x225.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div align=\"center\"></div>\r\n<h2>Party Buses Cincinnati OH</h2>\r\nYou may opt to start out your night of crazy fun at a dive bar, and Dana Gardens (45207) will work nicely. For the beer enthusiasts in your group, O\'Malley\'s in the Alley (45202) has an extensive selection. Northside Tavern (45223) is the place to be for the hipsters and music lovers, and Scene Ultra Lounge has a cool, jazzy late night crowd. And if your friends are in the mood for a great burger, don\'t miss Longworth\'s for some tasty munchies\r\n\r\nAfter you see downtown, you can move toward the outskirts and rub elbows with friendly locals enjoying a pint at their neighborhood tap. Finneytown and Lincoln Heights are a quick jaunt from the city, and White Oak is just a hop away. Blue Ash and Kenwood lie to the northeast of the city, and there is easy access to the laid back joints in these towns off Interstate 71. The always hopping bars in Sharonville and Hazelwood are also to the north.\r\n<h2>Party Bus Prices Cincinnati</h2>\r\nWhen you want to have an unforgettable night out in Cincinnati cheap party buses are available to take control at the wheel. Having a professional, trained driver to escort you and your friends throughout your night of partying is not only smart, but it is also much more convenient. A party bus company takes responsibility for all of the driving annoyances, such as filling up on gas, finding a parking spot and fighting traffic. The wisest decision you can make for your entire crowd is to rent a party bus in Cincinnati and clear your mind of all the driving concerns.\r\n\r\nYou might expect to pay a fortune for excellent customer service and a clean, premium Cincinnati Ohio party bus. Nothing could be further from the truth. With so many cheap party bus rentals Cincinnati and its charms are within your grasp. The last thing you want to worry about during your adventure in the city is having an empty wallet. Low party bus prices mean you can get your transportation needs settled and still have cash left over to have food, drinks and fun.', 'Cincinnati Party Bus', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cincinnati-party-bus', '', '', '2013-07-20 14:31:48', '2013-07-20 14:31:48', '', '0', 'http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/?page_id=293', '0', 'page', '', '0');
