INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES ('302', '1', '2013-07-18 15:41:54', '2013-07-18 15:41:54', '<h1>Corpus Christi Party Bus</h1>\r\nClimb aboard a Corpus Christi TX Party Bus for an unforgettable night. When your next special occasion deserves something extraordinary to make it memorable, you need to rent a party bus in Corpus Christi. It is an ideal way to see the sights and unique attractions in the city while you cruise along in the comfort of a premium vehicle. Plus, limo buses in Corpus Christi will escort you around as you hop around all the town\'s hippest clubs and cozy neighborhood pubs. All your worries will slip away as you enjoy the night with your family and friends on board a Corpus Christi party bus.\r\n\r\nStereo Music Bar &amp; Sushi Bar (78401) is nice way to get things rolling with some food in your stomach. To spend some time outdoors while sipping on cold brews, check out Dewey\'s Beer Garden. Theo\'s Billiards is a pool hall that also features dart boards and several TVs for watching sports. For an upscale dive bar, head over to Jack Ash\'s Drinkery (78411). If you want some faster paced nightlife, Bombay Lounge &amp; Grill (78414) should definitely be on your route.\r\n<table width=\"460\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://www.price4limo.com/limo-party-bus-fleet.html\"><img alt=\"Corpus Christi Party Buses and Limos\" src=\"http://www.price4limo.com/images/party-bus-limo-fleet.jpg\" width=\"454\" height=\"145\" border=\"0\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.price4limo.com/limo-party-bus-fleet.html\">Preview our Corpus Christi Party Bus and Limo Fleet.</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div align=\"center\"><img alt=\"Corpus Christi party bus\" src=\"http://www.price4limo.com/images/corpus-christi-party-bus.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<h2>Party Buses Corpus Christi TX</h2>\r\nOne idea for a circle tour of the area is to head north out of the city toward Portland. After a beer run, travel further up to Ingleside and Aransas Pass. You will get to see magnificent views of the bay and can have a drink or two on the beach. From Rockport, drive across the causeway to Port Aransas and the barrier islands. If you want to stick closer to town, Robstown lies just to the southwest of the city and has a charming city center. Mathis is a bit further north and west, but offer the opportunity to hang out by Lake Corpus Christi.\r\n\r\nYou might be tempted to think that a Corpus Christi Texas party bus rental would be expensive. Nothing could be further from the truth, and there is definitely something that anyone can afford. With cheap party bus rentals Corpus Christi hot spots are even easier to afford. You will have money left in your pocket to spend on food, drinks and entertainment because of low party bus prices. Plus, you will have no trouble convincing everyone in your party to donate a few bucks to the party cause. In Corpus Christi cheap party buses make all of the festivities budget friendly to everyone in your group.\r\n<h2>Party Bus Prices Corpus Christi</h2>\r\nTo many, the convenience of having a professional driver is even more important than the money. Having a fabulous time and mingling with your group is hard to do if you have to think about transportation. A party bus company takes care of all the hassles, like traffic, parking and gas.\r\n\r\nBachelor bashes and bachelorette ladies\' nights are perfect opportunities to get a limo bus rental, and let someone else do the driving. A prom party bus in Corpus Christi will get everyone to the dance safely and in style. The happy couple can enjoy their anniversary party with class while touring the town. If you\'re planning a retirement party for a co-worker, party buses in Corpus Christi TX can pick everyone up at the office and depart for an unforgettable night of crazy times. Whether you are just looking to whoop it up in town for a night or are celebrating a special occasion, a Corpus Christi Texas party bus fits the bill.', 'Corpus Christi Party Bus', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '298-revision-3', '', '', '2013-07-18 15:41:54', '2013-07-18 15:41:54', '', '298', 'http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/298-revision-3/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
