INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES ('308', '1', '2013-07-18 15:46:09', '2013-07-18 15:46:09', '<h1>Fort Wayne Party Bus</h1>\r\nCelebrate worry free with a Fort Wayne IN Party Bus. If you are in charge of planning a special occasion and want to make it something everyone will talk about for years, you need to rent a party bus in Fort Wayne. You can gather your friends and family, and prepare yourselves for an exciting night out on the town. Cruising around party buses in Fort Wayne IN enables your whole group to view the sights and attractions in the city in the comfort of a classy vehicle. When it comes time to stop for food and drinks, you can hit all the hot spots in your Fort Wayne Indiana party bus.\r\n\r\nWith all the celebrating you\'ll be doing, it\'s a good idea to start the night off with some food. The Green Frog Inn (46808) is known for its burgers and sandwiches. Henry\'s Restaurant does an amazing prime rib of beef that will have your mouth watering. If you\'d rather munch on some tasty pizza while catching the latest sports highlights, make your way over to Arena Bar &amp; Grill (46825). To crack up laughing at crazy skits and improve acts, Pierre\'s Comedy Club (46835) will leave you rolling in the aisles. For a pool tournament and bragging rights among your group, hit the Corner Pocket Pub.\r\n<table width=\"460\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/pink1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-482\" alt=\"pink1\" src=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/pink1-300x198.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"198\" /></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.price4limo.com/limo-party-bus-fleet.html\">\r\n</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div align=\"center\"></div>\r\n<h2>Party Buses Fort Wayne TX</h2>\r\nIf your plans include a trip to the airport, you can mosey out of