INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES ('365', '1', '2013-07-20 14:46:59', '2013-07-20 14:46:59', '<h1>Toledo Party Bus</h1>\nRock out all night in a Toledo OH Party Bus. When you think you\'ve seen and done it all, try something new and rent a Toledo Ohio Party Bus to cruise around town in style with your friends and family. There are tons of neighborhoods to explore, new favorite hangouts to discover, and clubs to dance the night away. With a Toledo Ohio Party Bus Rental, your crew can see all the sights and still have time for stops to experience the nightlife. Any bash is better when you have a driver from a Party bus Company to chauffeur you around town. It\'s your turn to relax, cut loose and share some thrilling times with your guests.\n\nIn a Toledo Party Bus, you make a once in a lifetime event even more special. For a large group outing, such as a bachelor or bachelorette party, check out a spacious Escalade Limo. A wedding achieves new levels of elegance with a sleek, Chrysler 300 Stretch Limo Bus Rental. If you want to tour around town to all the exclusive wine bars in Toledo Cheap Party Buses can get you there.\n<table width=\"460\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://www.price4limo.com/limo-party-bus-fleet.html\">\n</a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n&nbsp;\n<div align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/miami-1954-rolls-royce-phantom.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-188\" alt=\"miami-1954-rolls-royce-phantom\" src=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/miami-1954-rolls-royce-phantom.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"140\" /></a></div>\n<h2>Party Buses Toledo OH</h2>\nA Homecoming or Prom Party Bus in Toledo is the safest option for getting kids to the big dance. When you are getting together with the guys for the big sporting event or to rock out at a concert, the last thing you want to deal with is traffic and parking. A Hummer Limo will get you there and take care of the driving hassles. To get everyone into the Christmas spirit, venture around all the holiday light displays in Party Buses in Toledo OH.\n\nWith all these activities, you need to make time for food and drink stops. To load up on a tasty burger or some mouth watering barbeque, head to Shorty\'s True American Roadhouse (43623). If you want to grab a bite while watching the game and checking scores, stop off at Home Slice for a slice of pizza and pitcher of beer. Jed\'s at the Yard is another popular joint for sports fans, and the chicken wings are some of the best in the city. When you just want to grab a drink at a cozy neighborhood hangout, make your way to Wesley\'s Bar &amp; Grill (43624) and have one on the outdoor patio. For some groovy live music, don\'t miss the Ottawa Tavern (43604).\n<h2>Party Bus Prices Toledo</h2>\nIn the outskirts of town you will find plenty of action as well. Do your own pub crawl down the river and hit Rossford, Beverly and Perryville. Holland and Springfield are both on the way to the airport, so have a few cocktails to give them a good buzz before the flight. For awesome photo opportunities, cruise through the parks at Cedar Point and Maumee Bay, both very popular for shooting weddings pictures.\n\nWherever the night takes you, the exciting options are limitless. Because Party Bus prices are so low, the festivities can go on and on. Once you\'ve scored Cheap Party Bus Rentals Toledo is a city filled with spectacular sights and roaring nightlife. Hiring Limo Buses in Toledo will make sure you see it all. Take a load off and rent a party Bus in Toledo. Your only concern is to mingle with your guests and paint the town red.', 'Toledo Party Bus', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '362-autosave', '', '', '2013-07-20 14:46:59', '2013-07-20 14:46:59', '', '362', 'http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/362-autosave/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
