INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES ('369', '1', '2013-07-18 16:22:49', '2013-07-18 16:22:49', '<h1>Party Bus Dallas</h1>\r\nReserve a <strong>Dallas party bus service</strong> and make plans to head out to the third-largest city in Texas. Make plans to hang out with your friends and family to celebrate any occasion in one of our spacious and comfortable <strong>party buses in Dallas, TX</strong>. Whether you are looking to celebrate your bachelor party, sporting event, or wedding our fleet of charter buses in Dallas is more than willing to get the job done. Whether you need to reserve a<strong>Dallas party bus</strong> for a corporate event or birthday party you can find the right vehicle in our website. Visit Price 4 Limo and get a quote on any of our services regarding transportation throughout Dallas County, TX. Select from our library of available vehicles to help make your decision process a lot easier. With the variety of different <strong>party buses in Dallas</strong> you can get a quote within seconds once you know the day you need the vehicle for.\r\n<table width=\"460\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/ultimate-limo-dallas-escalade.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-196\" alt=\"ultimate-limo-dallas-escalade\" src=\"http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/ultimate-limo-dallas-escalade.jpg\" width=\"230\" height=\"144\" /></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Party Bus Rental Dallas</h2>\r\nWhen you reserve any of our <strong>party bus services in Dallas</strong> you can enjoy the comfortable leather interior seating and surround sound system available in all of our vehicles. One of the great things about riding inside our Dallas charter bus service is the opportunity to stand up and move to another location within the vehicle. Check out our 14 passeng