INSERT INTO wp_posts VALUES ('433', '1', '2013-07-20 08:47:56', '2013-07-20 08:47:56', '<h2>The Kentucky Derby – The Greatest Two Minutes In Sports</h2>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nThe Kentucky Derby has become the biggest racing event in the United States. With The Greatest Two Minutes in Sports you have a chance to enjoy the race that is going to be running for the 139th Kentucky Derby. With a lot of different horses looking to start their run for the triple crown you will be amazed by the many different horse breeds that are about to get on the track.\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://www.kentuckyderby.com/\"><img alt=\"kentucky derby 2013 churchill downs\" src=\"http://www.price4limo.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/kentucky-derby-churchill-downs.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"306\" /></a>Continue reading →</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Posted in Party Buses | Leave a comment\r\n<h2>Expanding Your Search In Price 4 Limo</h2>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>When it comes to searching on our website Price 4 Limo you have a few different ways of receiving information. One of our most popular, fastest, and easiest ways to get a quote is using our iframe (<em>pictured below</em>) where you can receive a quote in seconds! When you begin your research for a vehicle whether it is a party bus or limousine rental you want to make sure that you have a variety of options to select from on the type of service you are looking for.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nContinue reading →\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>Reserving A Limo or Party Bus</h2>\r\n<div>Posted on April 22, 2013 by Mark Sheer</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nIt is all about timing and availability when it comes to our selection of vehicle rentals. Here are some pointers to help you with deciding on when to make a reservation:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The earlier you reserve a party bus or limo rental the better odds that you will have the vehicle available for you and your guests at an affordable price.</li>\r\n	<li>Make sure that you and your friends know which type of vehicle you want to reserve.</li>\r\n	<li>Confirm the number of passengers before you reserve the vehicle. (You may need a larger one if the group grows or vice versa)</li>\r\n	<li>Have everyone chip in on the vehicle rental so you are not stuck paying for it all on your own.Continue reading →</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>More Than A Final Four Trip In Atlanta Georgia</h2>\r\n<div>Posted on April 4, 2013 by Mark Sheer</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe Final Four is this weekend in Atlanta Georgia and will be taking place inside the Georgia Dome which is home of the NFL Atlanta Falcons. The city is going to be jam packed with a lot of people and it is going to be an exciting time for all who are checking out the city and enjoying the games for the first time or returning to the city. You will find plenty of <b>things to do in Atlanta</b> whether you are on a family vacation or traveling with friends.\r\n\r\nContinue reading →\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>Reserving An Affordable Limo Rental</h2>\r\n<div>Posted on March 22, 2013 by Mark Sheer</div>\r\n<div>Reserving an <strong>affordable Limo Rental</strong> provides you with a luxury vehicle without having to spend a lot of money for an amazing evening in the city. What Price 4 Limo has been able to accomplish is provide an affordable Limo rental at a price that is not going to leave you with a hole in your pocket. We have dealt with a lot of different types of transportation services when it comes to reserving one of our many limousine rentals. As a transportation company we provide our customers with the best listing in their area.</div>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nWhen it comes to deciding on which vehicle you want to reserve it typically falls under the type of occasion you are looking to celebrate. You never want to <b>reserve a limo rental</b> that is going to be too expensive. We are able to provide a low cost wedding Limousine that will not hurt your pocket. We know that it is important to stay within your budget no matter what the occasion is. With bachelor and bachelorette parties you want to be able to reserve a vehicle and have plenty of money left over for the rest of the night as you make your way to your favorite night clubs and restaurants.\r\n<h2>Deciding on the right Limo Rental</h2>\r\nWe have a lot of different selections of affordable Limo rentals that will fit what you are looking for. We are more than just a party transportation company we provide a business travel service for all corporate events. Looking for an airport transfer service? Our chauffeurs provide you with a trip to the airport so you are early enough to get through airport security. When you speak with our customer service staff we help you with finding the right limo rental that you need at a price you can afford.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nPrice 4 Limo has a Limo rental reserved for a different number of passengers whether it is a ride for 2 or a ride for 16 passengers. You can find yourself traveling in a Hummer Limo rental with a lot of real estate inside the vehicle as you listen to music or turn on the television and watch your favorite shows. You do not want to reserve a Chrysler 300 Stretch Limo for a few hours and not have your friends chip in on the rental cost. Do not get stuck with the bill and have everyone chip in on the rental of one of our vehicles.\r\n<h2>Select The Right Limo Rental</h2>\r\nWhen it comes to selecting the right limo rental you want to make sure you select the right one and with our library of vehicles we make it easy for our guests to find the one they need. Talk with your family and friends on which is the one you would like. Narrow down  your choices to two and do not hesitate to select your rental soon, someone may be eyeing the same vehicle as you. From a 10 passenger Lincoln Stretch Limo to a 16 passenger Excursion we have a great variety of vehicles that you can select from to complete your travel plans. With our database of cheap limo services you have an option of choosing the right vehicle at the right price. We are your one stop shop for making a reservation and completing an order for a night on the town, wedding, corporate event, or birthday party. Whether you are just looking for a quote or planning to make a reservation our Price 4 Limo website can help you get all of your questions answered.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'The Kentucky Derby – The Greatest Two Minutes In Sports', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-kentucky-derby-the-greatest-two-minutes-in-sports', '', '', '2013-07-20 10:46:12', '2013-07-20 10:46:12', '', '0', 'http://myjobodesk.com/price4limo/?page_id=433', '0', 'page', '', '0');
